properties.Name: ChannelHoursOfOperation
properties.Description: The Channel hours of operation on a particular date at the site where it is located.

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: DayOfWeekId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Day Of Week.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate

Columns.Description: The closing or ending time of operation for the Channel.

Columns.Name: HolidayIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the associated date is a holiday.

Columns.Name: HolidayName
Columns.Description: The name of the associated holiday.

Columns.Name: ChannelHoursOfOperationNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding a channel hours of operation.
